sentences.english: An unhandled exception occurred during index analysis.
sentences.chinese: 索引分析時發生未處理的異常情況。

sentences.english: Generally, an uncured specimen has a hardness reading below normal.
sentences.chinese: 通常，未處理的樣品的硬度讀數會低於正常值。

sentences.english: You might also want to specify certain exceptions that are not handled.
sentences.chinese: 可能還要確定某些未處理的異常。

sentences.english: The default error page will be displayed whenever an unhandled exception occurs.
sentences.chinese: 一旦出現未處理的異常，就顯示該缺省的錯誤頁面。

sentences.english: An hourglass to indicate an unprocessed reservation request.
sentences.chinese: 一個沙漏，指示一個未處理的預訂請求。

sentences.english: My wish is that it crashes if any exception was unhandled.
sentences.chinese: 我希望它崩潰如果任何的例外是未處理的。

sentences.english: The surface microhardness was substantially increased compared with the untreated.
sentences.chinese: 表面顯微硬度較未處理的樣品明顯提高。

sentences.english: 1 detected an error condition which was not handled by the application.
sentences.chinese: 檢測到應用程序未處理的錯誤狀況。

sentences.english: The automation will stop because of an unhandled window.
sentences.chinese: 自動化會因爲未處理的窗口而停止。

sentences.english: Teeth-like crusher can take treated or untreated rolled pulp.
sentences.chinese: 粉碎機齒片式，可適應未處理卷漿和已處理卷漿。

sentences.english: Should the new exception supersede the earlier exception that has not yet been handled?
sentences.chinese: 新的異常應該取代仍未處理的早先的異常嗎？
